<!DOCTYPE html>
<html><!--
Features: 
- Opens to a page asking you to create or load a character.
- Creating a character pops up with a form to enter in the name, age, etc. (More customization to come)
- Loading a character loads the QuestLog page for that character
- The QuestLog page is the main page that will show the quest log
	- The questlog shows quests in order of creation (More options later)
	- Questlog should allow users to click on a box beside each task to indicate the task was 
	  completed and should be able to be clicked on again to uncomplete the task.
	- There should be a button that appears beside the quest when all the tasks are done that
	  says "Complete Quest"
		- Upon completion the exp rewards are given
		- Quest is moved to completed quests section of quest log
	- There should be an option at the top that says "Create Quest" that opens a pop-up on the
	  page that has the quest creation form
		- Form will have a box for the quest description
		- Form will have a box for a task
		- There will be a button "Add Task" that creates another task box
		- There will be a rewards section that asks what the experience rewards will be (More rewards options to come)
		- (Future) Set an end-date for the Quest
		- (Future) Set a "repeat upon completion" option
			- (Future) Increase the rewards by "X amount" upon repeat
		- (Future) Become available upon completion of "X Quest" AKA Quest Lines
- The Character page
	- Shows character info
	- Show character stats
	- Shows a character bio
	- (Future) Shows a picture of the character/user
	- (Future) Shows feats/skills/proficiencies and describes them
- (Future) The adventure map
	- Shows places the character has been
	- (Maybe) Has a short story for each place
	- (Maybe) Have pictures of the place
- (Maybe/Future) The adventuring party
	- This will make this a social media platform instead of personal journal
	- Can add people to your adventuring party and see how they're doing
- (Maybe/Future) The inventory
	- Allow you to budget and track spending
- (Future) The master
	- A page of motivational quotes to help you on your adventure
	- Tips and tricks
	- Workout routines
	- Local hikes and running routes
	- Study tricks/groups/textbooks
	- Meditation videos/tips/styles
	- Recipes, diets, etc.
- (Future) Connect FitBit to this app!	
-->

<!-- Put back end code in the head and front end in the body -->
<head>
<title>QuestLog</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="Questlog.css">
</head>	

<body>
	<h1>QuestLog</h1>
	
	<p id="NewQuest">Create New Quest</p>
	
	<button onclick="location.href='{% url 'script' %}'">Execute Script</button> <hr>
        {% if data %}
        
        {{data | safe}}

        {% endif %}
	
	<ul id="QuestList">
		<li>Quest 1</li>
		<ul>
			<li>Task 1</li>
			<li>Task 2</li>
			<li>Task 3</li>
		</ul>
		<p class="CompleteQuest">Complete Quest</p>
		<li>Quest 2</li>
		<ul>
			<li>Task 1</li>
			<li>Task 2</li>
			<li>Task 3</li>
		</ul>
		<p class="CompleteQuest">Complete Quest</p>
		<li>Quest 3</li>
		<ul>
			<li>Task 1</li>
			<li>Task 2</li>
			<li>Task 3</li>
		</ul>
		<p class="CompleteQuest">Complete Quest</p>
	</ul>
	


</body></html>